Package: metaphlanToPhyloseq
Title: Convert MetaPhlAn taxonomic profiles to phyloseq objects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jérémy", "Rotzetter", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-6076-7077"))
Description: Simple package to load MetaPhlAn taxonomic profiles, clean or
    filter them based on specified taxonomic rank or abundance threshold,
    and create a phyloseq object from them.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jrotzetter/metaphlanToPhyloseq
BugReports: https://github.com/jrotzetter/metaphlanToPhyloseq/issues
